title: Ep. - 210 - BELOW DECK AND REAL HOUSEWIVES REVIEW
description:
Colin Gooch is a golf professional from Kentucky and has watched every episode of Below Deck. He reviews this week’s episode. 

 

Anthony Lario is an actor, comedian, and podcast host and pretty fired up about Real Housewives of Orange County, Atlanta, and New Jersey this season. Kate and Anthony deep dive on what shows need some changes, and the future of the franchise. 

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
